cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.NE 

The paper combines two popular areas of research in computer science: generative adversarial networks (GANs) and interactive evolutionary computation (IEC). Therefore, it is likely to be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), graphics (cs.GR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, given the focus on GANs and image generation, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories.
